              <h1>-  Our Goals  - </h1>
              <p> At EQUILENS, our aim is to offer users a comprehensive understanding of social media platforms' positions on various social and humanitarian issues. We strive to showcase the neutrality of each platform by providing transparent and unbiased rankings based on thorough analysis and research. Our objective is to empower users to navigate the digital landscape with confidence, knowing they can rely on our ratings to assess the fairness and objectivity of the information they encounter online.</p>
              <p>Through our carefully curated rankings, we highlight how different platforms address issues such as human rights, environmental sustainability, diversity, and more. By presenting this information clearly and accessibly, we hope to encourage critical thinking and informed decision-making among users.</p>
